msgctxt "seo_title"
msgid "Plan Your Trip | Mozilla Festival 2026"
msgstr "Planen Sie Ihre Reise | Mozilla Festival 2026"

msgctxt "search_description"
msgid "Planning to join MozFest 2026 in Barcelona? Find travel tips, visa support, transport routes, and exclusive hotel deals for this year’s festival at Fabra i Coats."
msgstr "Planen Sie, am MozFest 2026 in Barcelona teilzunehmen? Finden Sie Reisetipps, Visa-Unterstützung, Transportwege und exklusive Hotelangebote für das diesjährige Festival bei Fabra i Coats."

msgctxt "title"
msgid "Plan Your Trip"
msgstr "Planen Sie Ihre Reise"

msgctxt "hero_title"
msgid "Plan Your Trip to Mozilla Festival 2026"
msgstr "Planen Sie Ihre Reise zum Mozilla Festival 2026"

msgctxt "hero_description"
msgid "Joining us in Barcelona? Here are travel tips to help you get ready."
msgstr "Kommen Sie zu uns nach Barcelona? Hier sind Reisetipps zusammengestellt, die Ihnen bei der Vorbereitung helfen."

msgctxt "hero_image_alt_text"
msgid "Barcelona skyline at sunset, with the spires of Barcelona Cathedral and the Sagrada Família rising above dense rooftops, hills behind."
msgstr "Die Skyline von Barcelona bei Sonnenuntergang, mit den Türmen der Kathedrale von Barcelona und der Sagrada Família, die sich über dichten Dächern und Hügeln erhebt."

msgctxt "body.6edde3ab-4317-402c-85ac-82f59f5a5464.title"
msgid "Key Information"
msgstr "Wichtige Informationen"

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d1964797-8efe-43dc-931e-d1e9f014fdc9.title"
msgid "Visa Requirements"
msgstr "Visabestimmungen"

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d1964797-8efe-43dc-931e-d1e9f014fdc9.content.ffa9c5b9-4f82-41a7-93c6-c143901c4c8f"
msgid ""
"<b>Step 1</b>: Before booking travel, <a id=\"a1\">check whether you need a visa to enter Spain</a>. If you're unsure, consider booking refundable travel and accommodation to give yourself "
"flexibility."
msgstr ""
"<b>Schritt 1</b>: Bevor Sie eine Reise anmelden, <a id=\"a1\">prüfen Sie, ob Sie für die Einreise nach Spanien ein Visum benötigen</a>. Wenn Sie sich nicht sicher sind, sollten Sie eine stornierbare"
" Reise und Unterbringung gebucht haben, um flexibel zu sein."

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d1964797-8efe-43dc-931e-d1e9f014fdc9.content.ffa9c5b9-4f82-41a7-93c6-c143901c4c8f"
msgid "<b>Step 2:</b> <a id=\"a1\">Confirm your passport is valid</a>. To travel into Spain, you will need your passport, and it should be:"
msgstr "<b>Schritt 2:</b> <a id=\"a1\">Bestätigen Sie die Gültigkeit Ihres Reisepasses</a>. Um nach Spanien einzureisen, benötigen Sie Ihren Pass, und er sollte:"

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d1964797-8efe-43dc-931e-d1e9f014fdc9.content.ffa9c5b9-4f82-41a7-93c6-c143901c4c8f"
msgid "Valid for at least three months beyond your departure date from the Schengen area"
msgstr "bis mindestens drei Monate nach Ihrem Ausreisedatum aus dem Schengen-Raum gültig sein"

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d1964797-8efe-43dc-931e-d1e9f014fdc9.content.ffa9c5b9-4f82-41a7-93c6-c143901c4c8f"
msgid "Issued within the last 10 years from the date you enter"
msgstr "innerhalb der letzten zehn Jahre vor dem Einreisedatum ausgestellt sein"

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d1964797-8efe-43dc-931e-d1e9f014fdc9.content.ffa9c5b9-4f82-41a7-93c6-c143901c4c8f"
msgid ""
"<b>Step 3</b>: Book your visa appointment using the relevant <a id=\"a1\">Spain Application Visa center</a> in your area. As soon as you know you're attending MozFest, book your visa appointment. It"
" can take time to secure and may delay your travel plans. For questions or support, contact <a id=\"a2\">festival@mozilla.org</a><a id=\"a3\">.</a>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Schritt 3</b>: Buchen Sie Ihren Visumstermin über das relevante <a id=\"a1\">Spanien-Visumzentrum</a> in Ihrer Nähe. Sobald Sie wissen, dass Sie das MozFest besuchen, sichern Sie sich Ihren "
"Visumsrermin. Dies kann einzige Zeit dauern und Ihre Reisepläne verzögern. Bei Fragen oder Unterstützung melden Sie sich unter <a id=\"a2\">festival@mozilla.org</a><a id=\"a3\">.</a>"

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d1964797-8efe-43dc-931e-d1e9f014fdc9.content.ffa9c5b9-4f82-41a7-93c6-c143901c4c8f"
msgid "<b>Step 4:</b> Request your visa support letter from us by emailing <a id=\"a1\">festival@mozillafoundation.org</a>"
msgstr "<b>Schritt 4:</b> Fordern Sie Ihren Unterstützungsbrief für Ihr Visum von uns per E-Mail an <a id=\"a1\">festival@mozillafoundation.org</a>"

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d1964797-8efe-43dc-931e-d1e9f014fdc9.content.ffa9c5b9-4f82-41a7-93c6-c143901c4c8f"
msgid ""
"<b>Step 5: Stay informed about</b> <a id=\"a1\"><b>ETIAS</b></a>, the new travel authorisation for visa-exempt travellers entering 30 European countries, which will be introduced in the last quarter"
" of 2026. It's not yet clear whether it will apply to our festival dates, so please check before you travel."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.fb0ecea0-a4be-4d3f-8a8a-0700ac7512ed.title"
msgid "Travel to Barcelona"
msgstr "Reise nach Barcelona"

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.fb0ecea0-a4be-4d3f-8a8a-0700ac7512ed.content.f7082bcb-2ac6-4df1-919f-77b1eddf0d63"
msgid "We advise you to book your travel and accommodation as soon as possible to take advantage of better rates."
msgstr "Wir empfehlen Ihnen, Ihre Reise und Unterkunft so schnell wie möglich zu buchen, um von besseren Preisen zu profitieren."

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.fb0ecea0-a4be-4d3f-8a8a-0700ac7512ed.content.f7082bcb-2ac6-4df1-919f-77b1eddf0d63"
msgid "By Air"
msgstr "Mit dem Flugzeug"

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.fb0ecea0-a4be-4d3f-8a8a-0700ac7512ed.content.f7082bcb-2ac6-4df1-919f-77b1eddf0d63"
msgid "Barcelona-El Prat Airport (BCN) is the city’s main international airport, offering direct flights from major global destinations."
msgstr "Der Flughafen Barcelona-El Prat (BCN) ist der wichtigste internationale Flughafen der Stadt und bietet Direktflüge von wichtigen globalen Zielen an."

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.fb0ecea0-a4be-4d3f-8a8a-0700ac7512ed.content.f7082bcb-2ac6-4df1-919f-77b1eddf0d63"
msgid "By Train"
msgstr "Mit dem Zug"

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.fb0ecea0-a4be-4d3f-8a8a-0700ac7512ed.content.f7082bcb-2ac6-4df1-919f-77b1eddf0d63"
msgid "Spain’s high-speed rail network links Barcelona to major European cities, with direct trains from Paris arriving in 6 and a half hours."
msgstr "Spaniens Hochgeschwindigkeitsbahnnetz verbindet Barcelona mit europäischen Großstädten; direkte Züge aus Paris kommen in 6,5 Stunden an."

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.fb0ecea0-a4be-4d3f-8a8a-0700ac7512ed.content.f7082bcb-2ac6-4df1-919f-77b1eddf0d63"
msgid ""
"More information on travelling to Spain is available on the <a id=\"a1\">Spanish Tourist Board</a> website. You can also find a list of Spanish consulates and embassies on the <a "
"id=\"a2\">Ministerio de Asuntos Exteriores, Unión Europea y Cooperación</a> website."
msgstr ""
"Weitere Informationen über Reisen nach Spanien finden Sie auf der Website <a id=\"a1\">des spanischen Tourismusverbandes</a>. Eine Liste der spanischen Konsulate und Botschaften finden Sie auch auf "
"der Website des <a id=\"a2\">Ministerio de Asuntos Exteriores, Unión Europea y Cooperación</a>."

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.fb0ecea0-a4be-4d3f-8a8a-0700ac7512ed.content.f7082bcb-2ac6-4df1-919f-77b1eddf0d63"
msgid "See hotel suggestions below"
msgstr "Im Folgenden finden Sie Hotelvorschläge"

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.8a68efc1-0647-4af8-a480-47bf5b440c33.title"
msgid "Travel from BCN Airport"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.8a68efc1-0647-4af8-a480-47bf5b440c33.content.96fcdc5d-8f8a-4a0a-9104-8493aa5208e8"
msgid "Barcelona-El Prat Airport (BCN) is the main international airport and is around 30–40 minutes from the festival venue depending on traffic and your ground transportation choice."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.8a68efc1-0647-4af8-a480-47bf5b440c33.content.96fcdc5d-8f8a-4a0a-9104-8493aa5208e8"
msgid ""
"ATMs and free Wifi are available throughout the terminals. If your phone plan doesn’t cover Spain, SIM card vendors are located in the arrivals area at BCN. You'll need your passport to register a "
"Spanish SIM. eSIMs (Airalo, Holafly, etc.) are a convenient alternative if your phone supports them and have been used successfully by the MozFest team."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.8a68efc1-0647-4af8-a480-47bf5b440c33.content.96fcdc5d-8f8a-4a0a-9104-8493aa5208e8"
msgid "Options from airport to in city:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.8a68efc1-0647-4af8-a480-47bf5b440c33.content.96fcdc5d-8f8a-4a0a-9104-8493aa5208e8"
msgid ""
"<b>Aerobús</b> — an express airport bus to major stops in central Barcelona. Runs every 5–10 minutes and the journey is around 35 minutes. Tickets are available on board, at machines, or <a "
"id=\"a1\">in advance online</a>."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.8a68efc1-0647-4af8-a480-47bf5b440c33.content.96fcdc5d-8f8a-4a0a-9104-8493aa5208e8"
msgid ""
"<b>Metro Line 9 Sud (L9S)</b> — runs directly from the airport (both Terminal 1 and Terminal 2 have their own metro stations). The general single ticket metro and bus option is not valid for the "
"metro line to El Prat Airport. For this route, a special “Airport Ticket” is required. If you plan to use public transport during your stay in Barcelona, the <a id=\"a1\">Hola Barcelona Travel "
"Card</a> is another option. This travel pass has multiple day options that include unlimited travel on all public transport, including the airport metro line."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.8a68efc1-0647-4af8-a480-47bf5b440c33.content.96fcdc5d-8f8a-4a0a-9104-8493aa5208e8"
msgid ""
"<b>Train (R2 Nord)</b> — runs from Terminal 2 to Sants, Passeig de Gràcia, and Clot stations. Journey is around 25 minutes. A standard train ticket does not include onward travel on the metro or bus"
" in Barcelona. The <a id=\"a1\">Hola Barcelona Travel Card</a> is handy for this option as it covers the train, metro, and buses.."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.8a68efc1-0647-4af8-a480-47bf5b440c33.content.96fcdc5d-8f8a-4a0a-9104-8493aa5208e8"
msgid ""
"<b>Taxi</b> — official taxis (black and yellow) wait at clearly marked ranks outside both terminals. A taxi to the city centre is typically €30–40 and most accept card payment. Freenow and Cabify "
"are available app-based ride options. Uber is also available though availability can be limited."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.1ba8d0e3-444c-4694-839f-7918e5eed484.title"
msgid "Public Transport"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.1ba8d0e3-444c-4694-839f-7918e5eed484.content.6e8ed539-7581-46ba-a775-7fcb24935ff4"
msgid ""
"Barcelona has an excellent public transport network covering metro, bus, tram, and suburban rail. <b>The venue is accessible by local train, metro and buses. The closest station is Sant "
"Andreu</b>,<b> served by the L1 (Red Line), R2, R2N, R11 as well as regional services.</b>"
msgstr ""
"Barcelona verfügt über ein hervorragendes öffentliches Verkehrsnetz, das U-Bahn, Bus, Straßenbahn und S-Bahn abdeckt. <b>Der Veranstaltungsort ist mit dem Nahverkehrszug, der U-Bahn und Bussen "
"erreichbar. Die nächstgelegene Haltestelle ist Sant Andreu,</b>,<b> bedient von der L1 (Rote Linie), R2, R2N, R11 sowie regionalen Verbindungen.</b>"

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.1ba8d0e3-444c-4694-839f-7918e5eed484.content.6e8ed539-7581-46ba-a775-7fcb24935ff4"
msgid "Tickets and travel cards"
msgstr "Tickets und Reisekarten"

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.1ba8d0e3-444c-4694-839f-7918e5eed484.content.6e8ed539-7581-46ba-a775-7fcb24935ff4"
msgid "<a id=\"a1\"><b>T-casual</b></a><b>:</b> 10 single rides on metro, bus, tram, and FGC trains within Zone 1 which covers the venue and central Barcelona. This is not valid on airport transfers"
msgstr ""
"<a id=\"a1\"><b>T-casual</b></a><b>:</b> 10 Einzelfahrten mit U-Bahn, Bus, Straßenbahn und FGC-Zügen innerhalb der Zone 1, die den Veranstaltungsort und das Zentrum von Barcelona abdeckt. Diese "
"Karte gilt nicht für Flughafentransfers"

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.1ba8d0e3-444c-4694-839f-7918e5eed484.content.6e8ed539-7581-46ba-a775-7fcb24935ff4"
msgid "<a id=\"a1\"><b>Hola Barcelona Travel Card</b></a><b>:</b> unlimited travel for 2, 3, 4, or 5 consecutive days. Includes airport transfers on the metro"
msgstr "<a id=\"a1\"><b>Hola Barcelona Travel Card</b></a><b>:</b> Unbegrenztes Reisen für 2, 3, 4 oder 5 aufeinanderfolgende Tage. Inklusive Flughafentransfer mit der U-Bahn"

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.1ba8d0e3-444c-4694-839f-7918e5eed484.content.6e8ed539-7581-46ba-a775-7fcb24935ff4"
msgid "Note that special fares can apply for airport transfers, always check that your ticket is valid before travelling to or from the airport."
msgstr "Beachten Sie, dass für Flughafentransfers Sondertarife gelten können. Überprüfen Sie immer, ob Ihr Ticket gültig ist, bevor Sie zum oder vom Flughafen reisen."

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.1ba8d0e3-444c-4694-839f-7918e5eed484.content.6e8ed539-7581-46ba-a775-7fcb24935ff4"
msgid "Navigation apps"
msgstr "Navigations-Apps"

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.1ba8d0e3-444c-4694-839f-7918e5eed484.content.6e8ed539-7581-46ba-a775-7fcb24935ff4"
msgid "<a id=\"a1\"><b>TMB App</b></a><b>:</b> Barcelona’s official public transport app for live metro, bus, and tram information"
msgstr "<a id=\"a1\"><b>TMB-App </b></a><b>:</b> Barcelonas offizielle App für öffentliche Verkehrsmittel mit Live-Informationen zu U-Bahn, Bus und Straßenbahn"

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.1ba8d0e3-444c-4694-839f-7918e5eed484.content.6e8ed539-7581-46ba-a775-7fcb24935ff4"
msgid "<a id=\"a1\"><b>Citymapper</b></a><b>:</b> Real time information and routes for public transport, taxis, cycling and walking across Barcelona"
msgstr "<a id=\"a1\"><b>Citymapper</b></a><b>:</b> Echtzeitinformationen und Routen für öffentliche Verkehrsmittel, Taxis, Radfahren und Zu-Fuß-Gehen in Barcelona"

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d11ef0ad-7fe2-4e55-9c4c-b42a8d3380c9.title"
msgid "Accessibility, Inclusion &amp; Wellbeing"
msgstr "Barrierefreiheit, Inklusion &amp; Wohlbefinden"

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d11ef0ad-7fe2-4e55-9c4c-b42a8d3380c9.content.79081ddd-cb5f-4da8-910c-51d054f5b32c"
msgid ""
"MozFest is meant to be for everyone. We want it to be welcoming, easy to navigate, and as safe as possible for all — across all genders, sexualities, faiths, abilities, and backgrounds. We have been"
" working closely with the venue and our production team to plan for the following:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d11ef0ad-7fe2-4e55-9c4c-b42a8d3380c9.content.79081ddd-cb5f-4da8-910c-51d054f5b32c"
msgid ""
"A marked <b>accessible route</b> runs through the venue, avoiding cobblestoned areas. The full route map will be published ahead of the festival. By mobility scooter, the longest journey across the "
"venue takes about 4 minutes, and the nearest metro station is about 3 minutes away."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d11ef0ad-7fe2-4e55-9c4c-b42a8d3380c9.content.79081ddd-cb5f-4da8-910c-51d054f5b32c"
msgid "<b>Elevators</b> are available in all main festival buildings and are tested to make sure people using mobility devices can enter and operate them easily."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d11ef0ad-7fe2-4e55-9c4c-b42a8d3380c9.content.79081ddd-cb5f-4da8-910c-51d054f5b32c"
msgid "Most <b>restrooms</b> at the venue are gender neutral. Accessible restrooms are also available and will be marked on the venue map."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d11ef0ad-7fe2-4e55-9c4c-b42a8d3380c9.content.79081ddd-cb5f-4da8-910c-51d054f5b32c"
msgid "Additional designated spaces are available for specific participant wellbeing needs:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d11ef0ad-7fe2-4e55-9c4c-b42a8d3380c9.content.79081ddd-cb5f-4da8-910c-51d054f5b32c"
msgid "A <b>quiet space</b> for silent prayer or reflection"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d11ef0ad-7fe2-4e55-9c4c-b42a8d3380c9.content.79081ddd-cb5f-4da8-910c-51d054f5b32c"
msgid "A <b>parent / carer space</b> with comfortable seating and changing facilities"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d11ef0ad-7fe2-4e55-9c4c-b42a8d3380c9.content.79081ddd-cb5f-4da8-910c-51d054f5b32c"
msgid "A <b>first aid station</b> staffed by trained medical professionals."
msgstr "Eine <b>Erste-Hilfe-Station</b> mit ausgebildeten medizinischen Fachkräften"

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d11ef0ad-7fe2-4e55-9c4c-b42a8d3380c9.content.79081ddd-cb5f-4da8-910c-51d054f5b32c"
msgid "A <b>pre-event accessibility guide</b> will be published closer to the festival, with detailed maps, lift locations, water stations, and dedicated space locations."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d11ef0ad-7fe2-4e55-9c4c-b42a8d3380c9.content.79081ddd-cb5f-4da8-910c-51d054f5b32c"
msgid ""
"<b>Before you travel:</b> If you have access needs we should know about or questions you'd like to talk through, please email <a id=\"a1\">festival@mozillafoundation.org</a> in advance so we can "
"plan with you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d11ef0ad-7fe2-4e55-9c4c-b42a8d3380c9.content.79081ddd-cb5f-4da8-910c-51d054f5b32c"
msgid ""
"Our onsite<b> Safety Team</b> will be present throughout the festival. Concerns around <a id=\"a1\">Community Participation Guidelines</a> violations can be raised confidentially at any time at our "
"information points or via our support contact number, which will be published closer to the event."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.80800d82-fabe-435c-bd67-ebe1b00c3571.title"
msgid "Travel Support"
msgstr "Reiseunterstützung"

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.80800d82-fabe-435c-bd67-ebe1b00c3571.content.a5a2ea44-ab21-4a34-b7f6-8f7838cd07ef"
msgid "A limited travel fund is available for facilitators whose session proposals are accepted through our Call for Proposals."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.80800d82-fabe-435c-bd67-ebe1b00c3571.content.a5a2ea44-ab21-4a34-b7f6-8f7838cd07ef"
msgid "We do not offer travel support for general participants or volunteers."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.80800d82-fabe-435c-bd67-ebe1b00c3571.content.a5a2ea44-ab21-4a34-b7f6-8f7838cd07ef"
msgid ""
"If you have an idea for a session, we encourage you to submit a proposal even if you don't currently have travel funding lined up. Travel support is reviewed as part of the selection process and "
"facilitators who need support can request it through their proposal application."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.80800d82-fabe-435c-bd67-ebe1b00c3571.content.a5a2ea44-ab21-4a34-b7f6-8f7838cd07ef"
msgid "Please note that funds are limited and support is not guaranteed for every accepted facilitator."
msgstr "Bitte beachten Sie, dass die Mittel begrenzt sind und die Unterstützung nicht für jeden akzeptierten Moderator garantiert ist."

msgctxt "body.975f2854-4f06-41d2-a968-6e21ecfb3d09.left_column.ed486685-ca31-4510-8268-33285747731e"
msgid "Where we'll be"
msgstr "Wo wir sein werden"

msgctxt "body.975f2854-4f06-41d2-a968-6e21ecfb3d09.left_column.ed486685-ca31-4510-8268-33285747731e"
msgid ""
"The Mozilla Festival will take place at the <a id=\"a1\">Recinte fabra i Coats</a>, ​​a former textile factory that today is now home to a mix of educational, cultural, social, housing and other "
"organizations."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.975f2854-4f06-41d2-a968-6e21ecfb3d09.left_column.ed486685-ca31-4510-8268-33285747731e"
msgid ""
"Fabra i Coats is 5 minutes walk from <a id=\"a1\">Sant Andreu</a> metro station on Line 1 (Red Line L1), this takes you directly to all the main sites across the city. It is easy to use, and you can"
" purchase a <a id=\"a2\">Hola Barcelona card</a> for the duration of your stay."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.975f2854-4f06-41d2-a968-6e21ecfb3d09.left_column.ed486685-ca31-4510-8268-33285747731e"
msgid "<b>Address:<br/></b><i>Carrer de Sant Adrià, Sant Andreu, 08030 Barcelona, Spain</i>"
msgstr "<b>Adresse:<br/></b><i>Carrer de Sant Adrià, Sant Andreu, 08030 Barcelona, Spanien</i>"

msgctxt "body.975f2854-4f06-41d2-a968-6e21ecfb3d09.right_column.08a8a99a-5861-417e-90fb-1b61c0a816c9.image.alt_text"
msgid "Fabra i Coats: brick industrial buildings with a tall chimney and graffiti, under a blue sky."
msgstr "Fabra i Coats: Backstein-Industriegebäude mit hohem Schornstein und Graffiti unter blauem Himmel."

msgctxt "body.b39a2a30-e463-4603-8dca-b8f275634fe7"
msgid "Where to stay"
msgstr "Unterkunft"

msgctxt "body.b39a2a30-e463-4603-8dca-b8f275634fe7"
msgid "There's a wide range of accommodation across the city to suit all budgets, but we advise you <b>book early</b> as rates can go up as summer approaches."
msgstr ""
"Es gibt eine große Auswahl an Unterkünften in der ganzen Stadt für jedes Budget, aber wir empfehlen Ihnen, <b>frühzeitig zu buchen</b>, da die Preise steigen können, wenn der Sommer näher rückt."

msgctxt "body.b39a2a30-e463-4603-8dca-b8f275634fe7"
msgid "We've partnered with a selection of hotels close to the venue to offer Mozilla Festival attendees special rates. Take a look at the participating hotels below:"
msgstr ""
"Wir haben uns mit einer Auswahl von Hotels in der Nähe des Veranstaltungsortes zusammengetan, um Mozilla Festival-Teilnehmern Sondertarife anzubieten. Werfen Sie einen Blick auf die untenstehenden "
"teilnehmenden Hotels:"

